What is Docker Networking?

Docker networking allows containers to:

Communicate with each other

Communicate with the host

Communicate across multiple hosts

Docker provides multiple network drivers to support different use cases.

ğŸ”¹ Types of Docker Networks

Bridge

Host

None

Overlay

